[
  {
    "scene": 1,
    "text": "The next time you sit down to eat,",
    "start": 0.0,
    "end": 1.5,
    "dur": 1.5
  },
  {
    "scene": 2,
    "text": "look at your plate.",
    "start": 1.86,
    "end": 2.48,
    "dur": 0.62
  },
  {
    "scene": 3,
    "text": "Someone grew that food with their hands.",
    "start": 3.08,
    "end": 4.9,
    "dur": 1.82
  },
  {
    "scene": 4,
    "text": "But almost nobody asks who.",
    "start": 5.46,
    "end": 6.92,
    "dur": 1.46
  },
  {
    "scene": 5,
    "text": "And the answer is strange.",
    "start": 7.4,
    "end": 8.6,
    "dur": 1.2
  },
  {
    "scene": 6,
    "text": "In America, the average farmer is now fifty-eight years old.",
    "start": 9.32,
    "end": 12.48,
    "dur": 3.16
  },
  {
    "scene": 7,
    "text": "More than forty percent are over sixty-five.",
    "start": 13.08,
    "end": 16.4,
    "dur": 3.32
  },
  {
    "scene": 8,
    "text": "Here in Thailand, it's no different.",
    "start": 16.4,
    "end": 17.5,
    "dur": 1.1
  },
  {
    "scene": 9,
    "text": "The people who feed us",
    "start": 18.12,
    "end": 19.12,
    "dur": 1.0
  },
  {
    "scene": 10,
    "text": "are quietly running out of time.",
    "start": 19.12,
    "end": 20.6,
    "dur": 1.48
  },
  {
    "scene": 11,
    "text": "So where is the next generation?",
    "start": 21.18,
    "end": 22.42,
    "dur": 1.24
  },
  {
    "scene": 12,
    "text": "I know — because I'm part of it.",
    "start": 23.1,
    "end": 24.86,
    "dur": 1.76
  },
  {
    "scene": 13,
    "text": "I grew up on an organic farm in Thailand.",
    "start": 25.56,
    "end": 27.9,
    "dur": 2.34
  },
  {
    "scene": 14,
    "text": "And one by one,",
    "start": 28.2,
    "end": 28.82,
    "dur": 0.62
  },
  {
    "scene": 15,
    "text": "I watched everyone my age leave.",
    "start": 29.34,
    "end": 31.16,
    "dur": 1.82
  },
  {
    "scene": 16,
    "text": "They went to the city.",
    "start": 31.8,
    "end": 32.78,
    "dur": 0.98
  },
  {
    "scene": 17,
    "text": "To offices. To screens.",
    "start": 33.26,
    "end": 34.6,
    "dur": 1.34
  },
  {
    "scene": 18,
    "text": "To money that arrives the same day.",
    "start": 35.36,
    "end": 37.0,
    "dur": 1.64
  },
  {
    "scene": 19,
    "text": "Farming looked like the past.",
    "start": 37.72,
    "end": 38.92,
    "dur": 1.2
  },
  {
    "scene": 20,
    "text": "Slow. Dirty. Invisible.",
    "start": 39.46,
    "end": 41.38,
    "dur": 1.92
  },
  {
    "scene": 21,
    "text": "I almost left too.",
    "start": 42.16,
    "end": 43.18,
    "dur": 1.02
  },
  {
    "scene": 22,
    "text": "But every morning,",
    "start": 43.86,
    "end": 44.54,
    "dur": 0.68
  },
  {
    "scene": 23,
    "text": "I still walk out before the sun.",
    "start": 44.54,
    "end": 46.24,
    "dur": 1.7
  },
  {
    "scene": 24,
    "text": "The soil is cold under my feet.",
    "start": 46.86,
    "end": 48.5,
    "dur": 1.64
  },
  {
    "scene": 25,
    "text": "I can smell the water",
    "start": 49.02,
    "end": 50.04,
    "dur": 1.02
  },
  {
    "scene": 26,
    "text": "before I can see the rows.",
    "start": 50.04,
    "end": 51.22,
    "dur": 1.18
  },
  {
    "scene": 27,
    "text": "And here's what no one told us:",
    "start": 51.92,
    "end": 53.5,
    "dur": 1.58
  },
  {
    "scene": 28,
    "text": "this isn't the past.",
    "start": 53.5,
    "end": 55.26,
    "dur": 1.76
  },
  {
    "scene": 29,
    "text": "While I plant,",
    "start": 55.9,
    "end": 56.66,
    "dur": 0.76
  },
  {
    "scene": 30,
    "text": "I'm teaching myself to code —",
    "start": 56.94,
    "end": 58.16,
    "dur": 1.22
  },
  {
    "scene": 31,
    "text": "to build with AI.",
    "start": 58.52,
    "end": 59.4,
    "dur": 0.88
  },
  {
    "scene": 32,
    "text": "The future doesn't have to replace the soil.",
    "start": 60.04,
    "end": 61.96,
    "dur": 1.92
  },
  {
    "scene": 33,
    "text": "It can grow out of it.",
    "start": 62.38,
    "end": 63.32,
    "dur": 0.94
  },
  {
    "scene": 34,
    "text": "So the next time you look at your plate,",
    "start": 63.86,
    "end": 65.34,
    "dur": 1.48
  },
  {
    "scene": 35,
    "text": "remember: someone chose to stay.",
    "start": 65.64,
    "end": 67.5,
    "dur": 1.86
  },
  {
    "scene": 36,
    "text": "Maybe the bravest thing my generation can do",
    "start": 68.22,
    "end": 70.4,
    "dur": 2.18
  },
  {
    "scene": 37,
    "text": "isn't leaving the land.",
    "start": 70.4,
    "end": 71.66,
    "dur": 1.26
  },
  {
    "scene": 38,
    "text": "It's coming back to it.",
    "start": 72.2,
    "end": 73.326,
    "dur": 1.126
  }
]